{
  "stem": "15577.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we came to the ghetto, we were going out to ghetto every morning in groups, because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] most of the places where the Jews were working with Germans were big groups, 100, 500, even 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It depend.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was with the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was with some organizations and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we're going out every morning at 5:00 in the morning and coming back organized.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And coming back at 6:00 or 5:00, 6:00 in the evening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to go everybody to-- his way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're going all together, patrolled by the Germans, by the SS, and so-- so this was the way of living.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody who came back was so tired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was almost no-- nothing more to do in the evenings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We young people were-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I see-- I think were-- were coming together more than the-- it was mostly so that people were coming together.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were living in two, three houses around them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there was mostly it was a curfew or people were afraid to go out in the night, because the Germans were drunk or so on-- so the patrolling Germans-- so they could shoot everybody if they made it, because they were drunk or just for fun.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we the youngsters, we did gather together more but not too much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then about the food, we got our rations-- food rations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We bought them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We bought them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were places where you could buy, but everything was rationed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People who were going out have two possibilities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The one possibility, which was used by all of us that we ate, we were able to by the Poles foods and to eat them outside.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
